[TITLE]
;;Project Title/Notes
Demonstrates the fix for a v5.1.013 parsing bug that incorrectly interpreted an ID name in the [REPORT]
section begining with "ALL" as the "ALL" keyword (with the same behavior for the "NONE" keyword). Running this
file shows that the entries "ALL_C1_3" and "ALL_C1_4" in the [REPORT] section are now recognized as link IDs.

[OPTIONS]
;;Option             Value
FLOW_UNITS           CMS
INFILTRATION         HORTON
FLOW_ROUTING         DYNWAVE
LINK_OFFSETS         DEPTH
MIN_SLOPE            0
ALLOW_PONDING        NO
SKIP_STEADY_STATE    NO

START_DATE           04/08/2008
START_TIME           10:00:00
REPORT_START_DATE    04/08/2008
REPORT_START_TIME    10:00:00
END_DATE             04/08/2008
END_TIME             22:00:00
SWEEP_START          01/01
SWEEP_END            12/31
DRY_DAYS             0
